    tmp = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.65 + v2 + 0.86) / wp.cos(tmp + 0.75)))
    v0 = (0.06 + 0.02)
    v0 = v1
    tmp = (0.17 - v2)
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.cos(0.48))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs(v1))
